  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "-        Conduct a baseline survey\r\n\r\n\t-        Introductory community meeting\r\n\r\n\t-        Two days pre orientation\r\n\r\n\t-        Develop the Udaan Curriculum\r\n\r\n\t-        One day review workshop with key stakeholders to get feedback on and finalize the curriculum\r\n\r\n\t-        A training package on the Udaan course for teachers\r\n\r\n\t-        Selection of sites for Udaan learning centers\r\n\r\n\t-        Exposure visit to Udaan India  \r\n\r\n\t-        Construction/rehabilitation\r\n\r\n\t-        Promote a gender friendly learning environment\r\n\r\n\t-        Conduct teachers training\r\n\r\n\t-        Management of Udaan learning centers\r\n\r\n\t-        Conduct two to three batches of 12 months Udaan courses\r\n\r\n\t-        Weekly review meetings facilitated by the Team Leader and Project Coordinator\r\n\r\n\t-        Form a “Friends of Udaan” group in public schools\r\n\r\n\t-        Organize monthly “Balika Sabha”\r\n\r\n\t-        Regular assessment of learning progress\r\n\r\n\t-        Support girls to participate in national exams\r\n\r\n\t-        Provide orientation to Mother Schools\r\n\r\n\t-        Provide orientation to girls\r\n\r\n\t-        Provide ingoing follow-up of girls from previous batches of Udaan\r\n\r\n\t-        Support vocational skills\r\n\r\n\t-        Provide scholarship"
    },
    "ne": null
